    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "-based table views, multiple row changes—that is, insertions, deletions, and moves—are animated simultaneously by surrounding calls to those method calls with "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1527288-beginupdates"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1526267-endupdates"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". These methods are nestable."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The selected rows are maintained during the series of insertions, deletions, moves, and scrolling. If a selected row is deleted, a selection changed notification occurs after "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1524655-removerowsatindexes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is called."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "It is not necessary to call "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1527288-beginupdates"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1526267-endupdates"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if only one insertion, deletion, or move is occurring and the table view is an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "-based table view. When using an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscell"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "-based table view, you must surround any insertion, deletion, or move in an update block for animations to occur."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The main reason for doing a batch update of changes to a table view is to avoid having the table animate unnecessarily."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Note that these methods should be called to reflect changes in your model; they do not make any underlying model changes."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "For "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscell"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "-based table views, it is required to call "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1527288-beginupdates"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " if you want to animate the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1532406-insertrowsatindexes"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1524655-removerowsatindexes"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", and "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1535835-moverowatindex"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
